    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior shows minor paint chips and some small surface scratches. The interior is clean, with light wear visible on the driver's seat. All mechanical systems are functional and have been maintained.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are solid, but you should expect some minor oil seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a cracked dashboard. It is a functional car that would benefit from some cosmetic TLC and a tune-up, but it is ready to drive home today.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to the most exacting standards of preservation. This vehicle remains in pristine condition, boasting an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original showroom luster. Every mechanical system has been subjected to a rigorous inspection to ensure peak operational performance, offering the discerning buyer a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled quality. We invite you to experience this masterwork of engineering firsthand.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty\u2014it's honestly in such incredible shape that it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that's practically brand new and looks stunning from every angle, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 1994 Supra Turbo is a textbook example of JZA80 engineering, preserved in museum-grade condition. Under the hood, the 2JZ-GTE power plant remains completely stock, retaining its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup and factory-spec boost levels. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, precise shifts, paired with a factory helical limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, with all OEM suspension geometry and bushings maintaining their factory-rated compliance. From the four-piston front calipers to the pristine underbody, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of 90s grand touring performance. No aftermarket modifications or electronic gremlins\u2014just pure, unadulterated Japanese performance with all VIN tags intact.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Immaculate interior. Full service history available. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2019 BMW M2 Competition is a collector-grade specimen that has been treated with obsessive care since day one. Finished in stunning Hockenheim Silver Metallic, the paint is entirely original and holds a deep, glass-like luster. The front end is completely free of stone chips or road rash, protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating that covers every exterior surface, including the factory 788M forged wheels. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the Black Dakota leather sport seats show no bolster wear, the carbon fiber trim is free of any delamination or scratches, and the original protective film remains on several interior sills. Mechanically, the car is in peak form. It features a comprehensive service history exclusively through BMW authorized centers, with all fluids changed ahead of schedule. There are zero modifications; the vehicle remains exactly as it left the factory. It has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or inclement weather. The sale is complete with the original window sticker, two master keys, all owner's manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. For the buyer seeking a flawless, 'as-new' driving experience without the showroom price tag, this vehicle is unparalleled.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a machine in pristine, showroom condition. Every aspect, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior, reflects a commitment to uncompromising quality. We invite discerning collectors and enthusiasts to inspect this peerless example of engineering and performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely in love with this car, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! It is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks like it just stepped out of a time capsule. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it polished and garage-kept, so it\u2019s sparkling clean inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel to it. If you're looking for a total gem that's been loved and pampered, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for you to come by and see how beautiful it is in person! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise mechanical engagement, paired with a refreshed M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been meticulously addressed, including documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension architecture remains true to factory specifications with updated bushings and dampers, ensuring optimal kinematic response and lateral grip. The exterior finish and interior Nappa leather are in concours-level state, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous mechanical stewardship.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
